Description
-----------

This CVar enables/disables the ability to run multiple instances of the
game on one computer.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    win_allowMultipleInstances [bool]

Parameters
----------

-   [bool] - Enables/disables the ability to run multiple instances of
    the game on one computer
    -   0 - Disabled
    -   1 - Enabled

