Notes
-----

This option can be useful for debugging in a multiplayer game as you can
start the [listen server](Listen_server "Listen server") and a
[client](Client "Client") on the same computer.

Multiple instances of a [dedicated
server](Dedicated_server "Dedicated server") can be run without setting
this parameter.

